   - **`set_db_conn()`**: Pluggable DB connection for persistence
   - **`_try_resume_from_db()`**: Looks up active sessions in `agent_sessions` table → calls `client.resume_session()` → falls back to fresh on failure
   - **`_persist_session()`**: Writes session info to `agent_sessions` table on creation

